autonomousSteps.script:
Intake.setIntakeSolState OPEN
Intake.setWantedIntakeState INTAKE
Hopper.setHopperState ON

# We set it to shoot 10 so that even in the case of a small jam we still shoot
VisionManager.shootBalls 7

@t 1.3
Intake.setIntakeSolState CLOSE
Intake.setWantedIntakeState OFF
Hopper.setHopperState OFF

@t 3.36
Intake.setIntakeSolState OPEN
Intake.setWantedIntakeState INTAKE
Hopper.setHopperState ON
